Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
    CHZ  Switzerland, West Europe.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P99  Nonclassifiable Establishments.
</IN>
<XX>
