last month. The Treasury said the overall level of official reserves rose by
Dollars 902m, taking reserves at the end of the month to Dollars 42.556bn
compared with Dollars 41.654bn at the end of December.
The dollar value of the UK's Ecu-denominated revolving credit facility,
agreed shortly before the pound left the exchange rate mechanism, rose by
Dollars 2m because of exchange rate changes.
