<DATELINE>
   JOHANNESBURG
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
LAW and Order Minister Hernus Kriel declared Johannesburg an emergency area
yesterday, giving police special search and arrest powers after the death of
two people in violent demonstrations by black taxi drivers, Reuter reports
from Johannesburg.
Mr Nelson Mandela's African National Congress condemned the declaration as
