</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A sharp drop in sales in November and December, plus further substantial
provisions against the cost of withdrawing from property development, pushed
Eleco Holdings into a loss of Pounds 2.21m for the six months to end-1992.
Directors said current trading was showing some improvement over last year.
